{
  "video_id": "D8S_LLnV3W8",
  "title": "Future tech will give you the benefits of city life anywhere | Julio Gil",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12780.0,
      "end_time": 16939.0,
      "text": "Today, more than half of the world&#39;s population lives in cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17820.0,
      "end_time": 21676.0,
      "text": "The urbanization process started in the late 1700s"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21700.0,
      "end_time": 23996.0,
      "text": "and has been increasing since then."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24200.0,
      "end_time": 27760.0,
      "text": "The prediction is that by 2050,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27100.0,
      "end_time": 30116.0,
      "text": "66 percent of the population will live in cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30140.0,
      "end_time": 33676.0,
      "text": "and the United Nations, the World Health Organization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33700.0,
      "end_time": 37156.0,
      "text": "the World Economic Forum, are warning us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 37180.0,
      "end_time": 39876.0,
      "text": "if we don&#39;t plan for the increased density,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39900.0,
      "end_time": 44995.0,
      "text": "current problems in our cities, like inequality, congestion, crime"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 45200.0,
      "end_time": 46396.0,
      "text": "can only get worse."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46420.0,
      "end_time": 49360.0,
      "text": "As a result, urban planners and city developers"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 49600.0,
      "end_time": 52596.0,
      "text": "are putting a lot of effort and creativity"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52620.0,
      "end_time": 56500.0,
      "text": "in designing our future, denser, bigger cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 57540.0,
      "end_time": 59396.0,
      "text": "But I have a different opinion."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 59420.0,
      "end_time": 63436.0,
      "text": "I think urbanization is actually reaching the end of its cycle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 63460.0,
      "end_time": 66780.0,
      "text": "and now people are going to start moving back to the countryside."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 67620.0,
      "end_time": 70636.0,
      "text": "And you may think, \"But what about the trend?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 70660.0,
      "end_time": 72636.0,
      "text": "Well, let me tell you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 72660.0,
      "end_time": 75100.0,
      "text": "socioeconomic trends don&#39;t last forever."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 76590.0,
      "end_time": 77756.0,
      "text": "You know, 12,000 years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 77780.0,
      "end_time": 80796.0,
      "text": "everybody was perfectly happy"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 80820.0,
      "end_time": 83836.0,
      "text": "roaming the land, hunting and gathering."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 83860.0,
      "end_time": 86516.0,
      "text": "And then, the trend changes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 86540.0,
      "end_time": 89996.0,
      "text": "and the new thing is to live in a farm and have cattle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 90200.0,
      "end_time": 91836.0,
      "text": "until it changes again."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 91860.0,
      "end_time": 94420.0,
      "text": "When we get to the industrial revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 95340.0,
      "end_time": 98916.0,
      "text": "Actually, that is what started the urbanization process."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 98940.0,
      "end_time": 100420.0,
      "text": "And you know what triggered it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 101340.0,
      "end_time": 103740.0,
      "text": "Steam power, machines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 104620.0,
      "end_time": 106436.0,
      "text": "new chemical processes --"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 106460.0,
      "end_time": 109660.0,
      "text": "in two words, technological innovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 111180.0,
      "end_time": 114420.0,
      "text": "And I believe technology can also bring the end of this cycle."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 115340.0,
      "end_time": 118276.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been working on innovation for most of my career."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 118300.0,
      "end_time": 120436.0,
      "text": "I love it. I love my job."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 120460.0,
      "end_time": 124556.0,
      "text": "It allows me to work with drones, with 3D printers and smart glasses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 124580.0,
      "end_time": 128636.0,
      "text": "and not just those you can buy in the shop but also prototypes."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 128660.0,
      "end_time": 130940.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a lot of fun sometimes."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 131820.0,
      "end_time": 133676.0,
      "text": "Now, some of these technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 133700.0,
      "end_time": 136796.0,
      "text": "are opening new possibilities that will radically change"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 136820.0,
      "end_time": 138596.0,
      "text": "the way we did things before"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 138620.0,
      "end_time": 140596.0,
      "text": "and in a few years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 140620.0,
      "end_time": 144516.0,
      "text": "they may allow us to enjoy the benefits of city life"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 144540.0,
      "end_time": 146196.0,
      "text": "from anywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 146220.0,
      "end_time": 147436.0,
      "text": "Think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 147460.0,
      "end_time": 151236.0,
      "text": "If you could live in a place with a lower crime rate"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 151260.0,
      "end_time": 152596.0,
      "text": "and more space"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 152620.0,
      "end_time": 154356.0,
      "text": "and a lower cost of living"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 154380.0,
      "end_time": 155780.0,
      "text": "and less traffic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 156500.0,
      "end_time": 158756.0,
      "text": "of course many people would want that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 158780.0,
      "end_time": 161476.0,
      "text": "but they feel they don&#39;t have a choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 161500.0,
      "end_time": 163260.0,
      "text": "You have to live in the city."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 164940.0,
      "end_time": 167596.0,
      "text": "Well, in the past, people moved to the cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 167620.0,
      "end_time": 170196.0,
      "text": "not because they loved the city itself"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 170220.0,
      "end_time": 172876.0,
      "text": "but for the things you could have in a city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 172900.0,
      "end_time": 174716.0,
      "text": "more job opportunities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 174740.0,
      "end_time": 176796.0,
      "text": "easier access to services and goods"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 176820.0,
      "end_time": 178190.0,
      "text": "and a rich social life."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 178860.0,
      "end_time": 180860.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s dive deeper."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 181620.0,
      "end_time": 184100.0,
      "text": "More jobs and career opportunities."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 184940.0,
      "end_time": 186276.0,
      "text": "Is that still true today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 186300.0,
      "end_time": 189476.0,
      "text": "because the office people are starting to realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 189500.0,
      "end_time": 193476.0,
      "text": "that working in the office and being in the office"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 193500.0,
      "end_time": 195140.0,
      "text": "may not be the same thing anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 196100.0,
      "end_time": 199236.0,
      "text": "According to a study by Global Workplace Analytics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 199260.0,
      "end_time": 203459.0,
      "text": "more than 80 percent of the US workforce would like to work from home."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 204500.0,
      "end_time": 208140.0,
      "text": "And do you know how much it costs for a company to even have an office?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 209600.0,
      "end_time": 212740.0,
      "text": "11,000 dollars per employee per year."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 213620.0,
      "end_time": 216396.0,
      "text": "If only half of those workers"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 216420.0,
      "end_time": 218780.0,
      "text": "would telework even 50 percent of the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 219860.0,
      "end_time": 224676.0,
      "text": "the savings in the states would exceed 500 billion dollars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 224700.0,
      "end_time": 229476.0,
      "text": "and it could reduce greenhouse gases by 54 million tons."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 229500.0,
      "end_time": 230756.0,
      "text": "That is the equivalent"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 230780.0,
      "end_time": 234860.0,
      "text": "of 10 million cars off the streets for a whole year."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 236140.0,
      "end_time": 239396.0,
      "text": "But even though most people would want to telework,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 239420.0,
      "end_time": 242956.0,
      "text": "current technology makes the experience isolating."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 242980.0,
      "end_time": 244236.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not comfortable."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 244260.0,
      "end_time": 246600.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t feel like being there."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 246620.0,
      "end_time": 249196.0,
      "text": "But that is going to change"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 249220.0,
      "end_time": 251516.0,
      "text": "by the convergence of two technologies:"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 251540.0,
      "end_time": 254540.0,
      "text": "augmented reality and telepresence robots."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 255420.0,
      "end_time": 257396.0,
      "text": "Augmented reality already today"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 257420.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260956.00000000003,
      "text": "allows you to take your office environment everywhere with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 260980.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264476.0,
      "text": "All you need is a wearable computer, a pair of smart glasses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 264500.0,
      "end_time": 266876.0,
      "text": "and you can take your emails and your spreadsheets"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 266900.0,
      "end_time": 268140.0,
      "text": "with you wherever you go."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 269600.0,
      "end_time": 273676.0,
      "text": "And video conferences and video calls have become very common these days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 273700.0,
      "end_time": 276116.0,
      "text": "but they still need improvement."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 276140.0,
      "end_time": 279600.0,
      "text": "I mean, all those little faces on a flat screen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 279900.0,
      "end_time": 282395.0,
      "text": "sometimes you don&#39;t even know who is talking."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 282420.0,
      "end_time": 287236.0,
      "text": "Now, we already have something way better than static videocalls:"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 287260.0,
      "end_time": 289916.0,
      "text": "your average telepresence robot."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 289940.0,
      "end_time": 292340.0,
      "text": "I call it tablet on a stick."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 292926.0,
      "end_time": 294750.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 294100.0,
      "end_time": 296836.0,
      "text": "You can control, you can move around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 296860.0,
      "end_time": 299360.0,
      "text": "you can control what you&#39;re looking at."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 299600.0,
      "end_time": 302340.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s way better, but far from perfect."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 302980.0,
      "end_time": 304196.0,
      "text": "You know how they say"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 304220.0,
      "end_time": 307260.0,
      "text": "that most human communication is nonverbal?"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 307820.0,
      "end_time": 310556.0,
      "text": "Well, the robot doesn&#39;t give you any of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 310580.0,
      "end_time": 311940.0,
      "text": "It looks like an alien."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 314200.0,
      "end_time": 316200.0,
      "text": "But with advances in augmented reality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 316860.0,
      "end_time": 320316.0,
      "text": "it will be easy to wrap the robot in a nice hologram"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 320340.0,
      "end_time": 323619.0,
      "text": "that actually looks and moves like a person."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 324340.0,
      "end_time": 325539.0,
      "text": "That will do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 326180.0,
      "end_time": 328236.0,
      "text": "Or else, forget the robot."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 328260.0,
      "end_time": 330236.0,
      "text": "We go full VR,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 330260.0,
      "end_time": 332580.0,
      "text": "and everybody meets in cyberspace."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 333220.0,
      "end_time": 336716.0,
      "text": "Give it a couple of years and that will feel so real,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 336740.0,
      "end_time": 338460.0,
      "text": "you won&#39;t tell the difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 339100.0,
      "end_time": 341660.0,
      "text": "So what was the next reason why people move to cities?"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 342900.0,
      "end_time": 344299.0,
      "text": "Access to services and goods."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 345660.0,
      "end_time": 347740.0,
      "text": "But today you can do all that online."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 348900.0,
      "end_time": 351600.0,
      "text": "According to a study made by comScore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 352220.0,
      "end_time": 354596.0,
      "text": "online shoppers in the US last year"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 354620.0,
      "end_time": 358100.0,
      "text": "did more than half of their retail purchases online,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 359200.0,
      "end_time": 362356.0,
      "text": "and the global market for e-commerce"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 362380.0,
      "end_time": 366356.0,
      "text": "is estimated to be at two trillion dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 366380.0,
      "end_time": 371596.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s expected to reach 2.38 by the end of 2017,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 371620.0,
      "end_time": 373200.0,
      "text": "according to eMarketer."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 374420.0,
      "end_time": 376140.0,
      "text": "Now, from a logistics standpoint,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 377600.0,
      "end_time": 378900.0,
      "text": "density is good for deliveries."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 380340.0,
      "end_time": 383200.0,
      "text": "Supplying goods to a shopping mall is easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 383660.0,
      "end_time": 386316.0,
      "text": "You can send big shipments to the shop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 386340.0,
      "end_time": 389476.0,
      "text": "and people will go there, pick it up and take it home themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 389500.0,
      "end_time": 392156.0,
      "text": "E-commerce means we need to ship onesies"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 392180.0,
      "end_time": 393956.0,
      "text": "and have them home delivered."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 393980.0,
      "end_time": 395236.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s more expensive."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 395260.0,
      "end_time": 398956.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s like the difference between having a birthday party for 20 people"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 398980.0,
      "end_time": 401760.0,
      "text": "or bringing a piece of the cake"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 401100.0,
      "end_time": 403740.0,
      "text": "to each of your 20 friends at their place."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 405600.0,
      "end_time": 407196.0,
      "text": "But at least in the city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 407220.0,
      "end_time": 408676.0,
      "text": "they live close to each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 408700.0,
      "end_time": 409940.0,
      "text": "Density helps."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 410740.0,
      "end_time": 414260.0,
      "text": "Now, e-commerce deliveries in the countryside,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 414980.0,
      "end_time": 416620.0,
      "text": "those take forever."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 417500.0,
      "end_time": 421956.0,
      "text": "The truck sometimes needs to drive miles between one address and the next one."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 421980.0,
      "end_time": 425700.0,
      "text": "Those are the most expensive deliveries of all."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 426860.0,
      "end_time": 429436.0,
      "text": "But we already have a solution for that:"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 429460.0,
      "end_time": 430876.0,
      "text": "drones."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 430900.0,
      "end_time": 434275.0,
      "text": "A vehicle carrying a squadron of drones."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 434300.0,
      "end_time": 436156.0,
      "text": "The driver does some of the deliveries"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 436180.0,
      "end_time": 439516.0,
      "text": "while the drones are flying back and forth from the truck as it moves."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 439540.0,
      "end_time": 442760.0,
      "text": "That way, the average cost for delivery is reduced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 442100.0,
      "end_time": 443580.0,
      "text": "and voila:"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 444620.0,
      "end_time": 447820.0,
      "text": "affordable e-commerce services in the countryside."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 448660.0,
      "end_time": 449996.0,
      "text": "You will see:"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 450200.0,
      "end_time": 451756.0,
      "text": "the new homes of our teleworkers"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 451780.0,
      "end_time": 454179.0,
      "text": "will probably have a drone pod in the yard."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 455460.0,
      "end_time": 458360.0,
      "text": "So once the final mile delivery is not a problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 458600.0,
      "end_time": 460660.0,
      "text": "you don&#39;t need to be in the city to buy things anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 461900.0,
      "end_time": 463116.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s two."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 463140.0,
      "end_time": 465820.0,
      "text": "Now, what was the third reason why people move to cities?"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 466380.0,
      "end_time": 467580.0,
      "text": "A rich social life."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 468620.0,
      "end_time": 471156.0,
      "text": "They would need to be in the city for that these days."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 471180.0,
      "end_time": 473236.0,
      "text": "Because people these days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 473260.0,
      "end_time": 476635.0,
      "text": "they make friends, they chat, gossip and flirt"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 476660.0,
      "end_time": 478476.0,
      "text": "from the comfort of their sofa."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 478500.0,
      "end_time": 479836.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 479860.0,
      "end_time": 482276.0,
      "text": "And while wearing their favorite pajamas."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 482300.0,
      "end_time": 483596.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 483620.0,
      "end_time": 487740.0,
      "text": "There are over two billion active social media users in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 488380.0,
      "end_time": 491676.0,
      "text": "In a way, that makes you think like we are connected"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 491700.0,
      "end_time": 492916.0,
      "text": "no matter where we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 492940.0,
      "end_time": 495236.0,
      "text": "But OK, not completely."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 495260.0,
      "end_time": 498700.0,
      "text": "Sometimes you still need some real human contact."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 499700.0,
      "end_time": 503596.0,
      "text": "Ironically, the city, with its population density,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 503620.0,
      "end_time": 505620.0,
      "text": "is not always the best for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 506580.0,
      "end_time": 509596.0,
      "text": "Actually, as social groups become smaller,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 509620.0,
      "end_time": 511236.0,
      "text": "they grow stronger."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 511260.0,
      "end_time": 513476.0,
      "text": "A recent study made in the UK"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 513500.0,
      "end_time": 515635.0,
      "text": "by the Office for National Statistics"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 515659.0,
      "end_time": 518515.0,
      "text": "showed a higher life satisfaction rating"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 518539.0,
      "end_time": 520260.0,
      "text": "among people living in rural areas."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 521860.0,
      "end_time": 525116.0,
      "text": "So as people settle in the countryside,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 525140.0,
      "end_time": 528116.0,
      "text": "well, they will buy local groceries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 528140.0,
      "end_time": 529955.0,
      "text": "fresh groceries, foodstuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 529979.0,
      "end_time": 531180.0,
      "text": "maintenance services."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 532100.0,
      "end_time": 537340.0,
      "text": "So handymen, small workshops, service companies will thrive."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 537820.0,
      "end_time": 540276.0,
      "text": "Maybe some of the industrial workers from the cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 540300.0,
      "end_time": 541620.0,
      "text": "displaced by the automation"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 542580.0,
      "end_time": 544916.0,
      "text": "will find a nice alternative job here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 544940.0,
      "end_time": 546140.0,
      "text": "and they will move too."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 547700.0,
      "end_time": 549556.0,
      "text": "And as people move to the countryside,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 549580.0,
      "end_time": 551236.0,
      "text": "how is that going to be?"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 551260.0,
      "end_time": 554360.0,
      "text": "Think about autonomous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 554600.0,
      "end_time": 556116.0,
      "text": "off-the-grid houses with solar panels,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 556140.0,
      "end_time": 559860.0,
      "text": "with wind turbines and waste recycling utilities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 560700.0,
      "end_time": 565916.0,
      "text": "our new homes producing their own energy and using it to also power the family car."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 565940.0,
      "end_time": 570360.0,
      "text": "I mean, cities have always been regarded as being more energy-efficient,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 570600.0,
      "end_time": 571315.0,
      "text": "but let me tell you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 571340.0,
      "end_time": 573820.0,
      "text": "repopulating the countryside can be eco too."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 576500.0,
      "end_time": 580220.0,
      "text": "By now, you&#39;re probably thinking of all the advantages of country living."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 580860.0,
      "end_time": 583760.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 583100.0,
      "end_time": 584356.0,
      "text": "I did it myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 584380.0,
      "end_time": 587915.0,
      "text": "Six years ago, my wife and I, we packed our stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 587940.0,
      "end_time": 589876.0,
      "text": "we sold our little apartment in Spain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 589900.0,
      "end_time": 594996.0,
      "text": "and for the same money we bought a house with a garden"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 595200.0,
      "end_time": 597596.0,
      "text": "and little birds that come singing in the morning."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 597620.0,
      "end_time": 599760.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 599100.0,
      "end_time": 601676.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s so nice there."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 601700.0,
      "end_time": 604676.0,
      "text": "And we live in a small village, not really the countryside yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 604700.0,
      "end_time": 606876.0,
      "text": "That is going to be my next move:"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 606900.0,
      "end_time": 609116.0,
      "text": "a refurbished farmhouse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 609140.0,
      "end_time": 611340.0,
      "text": "not too far from a city, not too close."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 612200.0,
      "end_time": 615236.0,
      "text": "And now we&#39;ll make sure to have a good spot for drones to land."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 615260.0,
      "end_time": 616436.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 616460.0,
      "end_time": 618196.0,
      "text": "But hey, that&#39;s me."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 618220.0,
      "end_time": 619476.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t have to be you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 619500.0,
      "end_time": 622236.0,
      "text": "because it would seem like I&#39;m trying to convince somebody"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 622260.0,
      "end_time": 623756.0,
      "text": "to come join us in the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 623780.0,
      "end_time": 624996.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 625200.0,
      "end_time": 626396.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 626420.0,
      "end_time": 628750.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t need more people to come."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 628100.0,
      "end_time": 629916.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 629940.0,
      "end_time": 631716.0,
      "text": "I just think they will"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 631740.0,
      "end_time": 635100.0,
      "text": "once they realize they can have the same benefits the city has."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 635896.0,
      "end_time": 637516.0,
      "text": "But if you don&#39;t like the country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 637540.0,
      "end_time": 639000.0,
      "text": "I have good news for you, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 639700.0,
      "end_time": 641620.0,
      "text": "Cities will not disappear."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 642460.0,
      "end_time": 643716.0,
      "text": "But as people move out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 643740.0,
      "end_time": 647660.0,
      "text": "a lower density will help them recover a better flow and balance."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 649100.0,
      "end_time": 652700.0,
      "text": "Anyway, I guess now you have some thinking to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 653780.0,
      "end_time": 656760.0,
      "text": "Do you still think you need to live in the city?"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 656100.0,
      "end_time": 657700.0,
      "text": "And more importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 658340.0,
      "end_time": 659540.0,
      "text": "do you want to?"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 660620.0,
      "end_time": 661836.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 661860.0,
      "end_time": 665860.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}